color red, 2KGI_structure and chain A and resi 22
color red, 2KGI_structure and chain A and resi 23
color red, 2KGI_structure and chain A and resi 29
color red, 2KGI_structure and chain A and resi 30
color red, 2KGI_structure and chain A and resi 32
color red, 2KGI_structure and chain A and resi 36
color red, 2KGI_structure and chain A and resi 42
